{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ff976e50c8","title":"对武汉事件的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ee543d9987","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"ff976e50c8"}],"tags":[{"id":"0d8f653275","name":"武汉地区无产阶级革命派百万雄师联络站（百万雄师）","type":"人物"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/50-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji50":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"824b0ade31","type":"title","text":"对武没事件的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"ff976e50c8"},{"id":"e320605054","type":"paragraph","text":"本来军内的问题没有机会解决，武汉问题发生了，就有机会解决了，机会是他们给的。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"ff976e50c8"},{"id":"648829b49c","type":"paragraph","text":"全国都应该从武汉事件中学习。全国支持武汉地区，武汉地区的斗争推动了全国的工作。一年来发生了天翻地覆的变化，当然有点乱。这里乱那里也乱，没有什么关系。像武汉这是很好的事，矛盾暴露了就好解决","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"ff976e50c8"},{"id":"2681caec15","type":"paragraph","text":"武汉一小摄人的叛变行为可以使全国的解放军、革命造反派、群众组织从中得到教育。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"ff976e50c8"},{"id":"0ab88e5b77","type":"paragraph","text":"这次文化大革命损失是最小最小最小的，成绩是最大最大最大的。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"ff976e50c8"},{"id":"aa6f83438d","type":"paragraph","text":"对“百万雄师”一个也不抓，几个坏头头让他们自己检举。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"ff976e50c8"}],"page":{"id":"9fdd022bce","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"ff976e50c8","start":37,"end":37}}}},"__N_SSG":true}